'''蛋白质合成GTP酶'''（{{lang-en|Protein-synthesizing GTPases}}，{{EC number|3.6.5.3}}）是指许多参与[[mRNA|mRNA]]翻译为蛋白质的[[起始因子|起始因子]]（IF）、[[延伸因子|延伸因子]]（EF）和[[释放因子|释放因子]]（RF），其系统名为''GTP phosphohydrolase (mRNA-translation-assisting)''<ref>{{cite journal | title = GTP interacts with the γ-subunit of eukaryotic initiation factor EIF-2 |author = Kurzchalia, T.V., Bommer, U.A., Babkina, G.T. and Karpova, G.G. |journal = FEBS Lett. |date = 1984 |volume = 175 |pages = 313-316 |pmid = 6566615 |issue=2}}</ref><ref>{{cite journal | title = Termination of translation in eukaryotes |author = Kisselev, L.L. and Frolova, L.Yu. |journal = Biochem. Cell Biol. |date = 1995 |volume = 73 |pages = 1079-1086 |pmid = 8722024 |issue=11-12}}</ref><ref>{{cite journal | title = Hydrolysis of GTP by elongation factor G drives tRNA movement on the ribosome |author = Rodnina, M.V., Savelsberg, A., Katunin, V.I. and Wintermeyer, W. |journal = Nature |date = 1997 |volume = 385 |pages = 37-41 |pmid = 8985244 |doi=10.1038/385037a0 |issue=6611}}</ref><ref>{{cite journal | title = Release factor RF3 in <em>E. coli</em> accelerates the dissociation of release factors RF1 and RF2 from the ribosome in a GTP-dependent manner |author = Freistroffer, D.V., Pavlov, M.Y., MacDougall, J., Buckingham, R.H. and Ehrenberg, M. |journal = EMBO J. |date = 1997 |volume = 16 |pages = 4126-4133 |pmid = 9233821 |doi=10.1093/emboj/16.13.4126}}</ref><ref>{{cite journal | title = EF-Tu, a GTPase odyssey |author = Krab, I.M. and Parmeggiani, A. |journal = Biochim. Biophys. Acta |date = 1998 |volume = 1443 |pages = 1-22 |pmid = 9838020 |issue=1-2}}</ref>，包括翻译的[[起始因子|起始因子]]如[[IF-2|IF-2]]和[[延伸因子|延伸因子]]如[[EF-Tu|EF-Tu]]。

